Bases: django.db.models.Model

Data management class.

DataID:

Primary Key with hash

Process:

Link to the process that created this entry

Type:

Type of data, defined in another enum

Data:

The data itself

Details:

Meta data and other information

CreatedBy:

Who created this data

ContentID:

ID of a file for example, makes searching easier

CreatedWhen:

Automatically assigned date and time(UTC+0) when the entry is created

UpdatedWhen:

Date and time at which the entry was updated

AccessedWhen:

Last date and time the data was fetched from the database, automatically set
